title: Unranked to Somewhere Nice | Support LF ADC for DUO-Q
body:
Hey Guys This is Dave.
I've been playing League for quiet a while now, as a Support Main, but i never really got into playing ranked.
So im looking for a ADC Buddy to share the Botlane with, to improve and start climbing together.
I'm a nice Dude from Germany, so good English is perfect, german is even better^^
Champions I play are Thresh, Bard, Braum, Janna, Taric and some Others.

So if you want to join my Journey from Unranked to somewhere nice add me in Game and drop a Message : )
Summonername: FmlSheWasJust13
